round-size:cover;-o-background-size:cover;background-size:cover;padding: 0px 14% 0px 14%;"><div class="imageframe-align-center"><span class=" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-227 hover-type-none"><img width="578" height="508" title="generationwork-responsive" src="/content/images/wordpress/2019/09/generationwork-responsive.png" class="img-responsive wp-image-25813" srcset="/content/images/wordpress/2019/09/generationwork-responsive-200x176.png 200w, /content/images/wordpress/2019/09/generationwork-responsive-400x352.png 400w, /content/images/wordpress/2019/09/generationwork-responsive.png 578w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 578px" /></span></div><div class="fusion-clearfix"></div></div></div></div></div><div class="fusion-fullwidth fullwidth-box fusion-builder-row-395 nonhundred-percent-fullwidth non-hundred-percent-height-scrolling" style="background-color: #f5f5f5;background-position: center center;background-repeat: no-repeat;padding-top:5%;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:5%;padding-left:0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;border-width: 0px 0px 0px 0px;border-color:#ecefef;border-style:solid;" ><div class="fusion-builder-row fusion-row"><div class="fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion-builder-column-804 fusion_builder_column_1_1 1_1 fusion-one-full fusion-column-first fusion-column-last" style="margin-top:25px;margin-bottom:25px;"><div class="fusion-column-wrapper fusion-flex-column-wrapper-legacy" style="background-position:left top;background-repeat:no-repeat;-webkit-background-size:cover;-moz-background-size:cover;-o-background-size:cover;background-size:cover;padding: 0px 14% 0px 14%;"><div class="fusion-text fusion-text-441"><p><strong>Problem</strong>: This brand-new consultancy needed an online presence quickly to support their work. Their offerings were still new, so there was not a lot of written material to start from.</p>
<p><strong>Solution</strong>: We rightsized their offering to get their website launched quickly. Their ideas inspired us to create a simple, clear, and – dare I say – stunning website.</p>
<p><strong>Impact</strong>: “After my project kick-off meeting my confidence soared. They asked the right questions, cut through my stories and excess, and got to the core of what I needed to say and to whom. The narrative work led to a smart site design and created what I think is a stunning website that communicates both emotionally and logically what I do and who I do it for. I’m delighted, confident and ready to roar! … Or at least to go get some more business.&#8221;</p>
<p>&#8211; <span style="font-weight: 400;">Jessie Newburn, Principal, GenerationsWork</span></p>
